{"type":"message","id":"087bf2a0","parentId":"fda51d22","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:52:00.810Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is an organizational chart/role definition file for a team of \"shrimp\" agents. Let me summarize what I've learned:\n\n- 0: 总经理 - General Manager\n- 1: 品牌展示虾 - Branding\n- 2: 引流获客虾 - Lead Generation\n- 3: 短视频虾 - Short Video\n- 3+: 私域运营虾 - Private Operations\n- 4A: 普通资质销售虾 - Standard Sales\n- 4B: 大客户销售虾 - Key Account Sales (this is my role!)\n- 5A: 普通资质代办虾 - Standard Processor\n- 5B: 大客户代办虾 - Key Account Processor\n- 6: 售后维系虾 - After Sales\n- 7: 数据诊断分析虾 - Data Analyst\n- 8: 机动应急打杂虾 - All-round Support\n\nSo I'm agent 4B - Key Account Sales Shrimp. The user earlier defined my specific responsibilities. Now I have the full organizational context.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已学习！这是团队架构表，整理如下：\n\n| 编号 | 岗位 | Agent ID |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 0 | 总经理 | General_Manager_Shrimp |\n| 1 | 品牌展示虾 | Branding_Shrimp |\n| 2 | 引流获客虾 | Lead_Gen_Shrimp |\n| 3 | 短视频虾 | Short_Video_Shrimp |\n| 3+ | 私域运营虾 | Private_Ops_Shrimp |\n| 4A | 普通资质销售虾 | Standard_Sales_Shrimp |\n| **4B** | **大客户销售虾** | **Key_Account_Sales_Shrimp** ← 我 |\n| 5A | 普通资质代办虾 | Standard_Processor_Shrimp |\n| 5B | 大客户代办虾 | Key_Account_Processor_Shrimp |\n| 6 | 售后维系虾 | After_sales_Shrimp |\n| 7 | 数据诊断分析虾 | Data_Analyst_Shrimp |\n| 8 | 机动应急打杂虾 | All_round_Support_Shrimp |\n\n我作为 **4B 大客户销售虾**，向上对接总经理，向下协同 5A/5B 代办虾，并与其他岗位配合获取线索和完成销售闭环。记住了 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":302,"output":705,"cacheRead":19707,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20714,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776750712160,"responseId":"063643783505443727698d413ca639f3"}}
